It has it all Waterfront, Dock, Pool, all Upgrades and one of the best things nothing but Florida Reserve woodlands behind you just water and forest. Keep your Boat and Water Toys in the  canal off  your dock and off you go out to the gulf. Crab and Fish of your Dock and right to the grill. This 3 story home is turn key and ready to go why build when this home is still NEW. So much to Show and tell so come tour this home any time.
